Package com.flipkart.business

Interface GymOwnerService

All Known Implementing Classes:
GymOwnerServiceOperations
public interface GymOwnerService
Interface representing the operations that a Gym Owner can perform. Includes methods for adding gyms, viewing owned gyms, validating gym owners, and updating gym owner details.
Author:
Shriya, Shreya k
